{"id": 529, "genre": 1001, "title": "为了（假装）战胜自己，你都做过哪些事？", "description": "啊！我的心，打满了鸡血！To be a better man !", "record_count": 3501, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201606071943238NrjocvPpfkmuFDO.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-09-15T12:08:41Z", "options": [{"id": 12033, "content": "我一个文科生买了五十本计算机的书。我变成了牛逼程序员", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 189428}, {"id": 13059, "content": "淘宝卸了重装装了又卸 不断循环", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 198203}, {"id": 12292, "content": "想做的事情到自己手上的时候 就不想做 对着自己 妈的老子做完了 然后就没有然后了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 191487}, {"id": 13060, "content": "dota2卸载 重装", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 201110}, {"id": 13316, "content": "屏蔽他的空间，然后还是手贱去看看?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205098}, {"id": 16132, "content": "失恋以后决心出国，我卸载了所有游戏，把iPad特意不带到学校，改了所有社交软件的简介签名。关注了好多学英语的公众号～～然而，并没有什么卵用。人都是贱的??也是够了（）", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 237689}, {"id": 13063, "content": "用手摸毛毛虫…", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 201262}, {"id": 13066, "content": "每次放假回家都得这个会用那个会用…然后带了一大堆东西 结果什么都没用???", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 201320}, {"id": 14353, "content": "脑补一下自己多牛b，这个计划或者说梦想完成了多吊，然后继续发呆脑补下一个。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219689}, {"id": 12306, "content": "手机上卸载聊天软件后看起了漫画", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 185539}, {"id": 12065, "content": "坚持药不能停", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 172394}, {"id": 17699, "content": "去考雅思啊，一下午坐3趟过山车啊，报名参加Debating啊，去酒吧蒲啊，学抽烟猜拳掷骰子啊，去滑翔啊，去坐降落伞啊……学数学啊??", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 255130}, {"id": 16166, "content": "把头发剪得短短的，让自己重新做人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241975}, {"id": 12090, "content": "已经大学了，每次放假回家已经大包小包的了，还要在书包里塞两本书，塞一支笔，私心想着回家看看，结果到了开学也没开过书包←_←", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 188774}, {"id": 13371, "content": "为了瘦吃了半个月燕麦 瘦了十斤 之后又吃回去了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205109}, {"id": 14143, "content": "说好不要找她，手贱还主动找", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 216228}, {"id": 12096, "content": "每次做好一大堆计划，设置一大堆提醒。然后精神恍惚间，全部取消了！", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211112pFyo58ZJb1sBGWYD.jpg", "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 190036}, {"id": 12352, "content": "终究还是败给了懒惰。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 191894}, {"id": 14660, "content": "好多，但一开始真的想做好的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 216564}, {"id": 12101, "content": "告诉自己，一定要忍住不吃东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 187014}, {"id": 12621, "content": "默默买了几本书，然后没有然后了。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 195063}, {"id": 11869, "content": "强迫自己相信自己能做好", "image": null, "praise_count": 106, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 165834}, {"id": 12125, "content": "原来我不是一个人hhh", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 153982}, {"id": 11870, "content": "卸载各种app，然后默默装上", "image": null, "praise_count": 395, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 178863}, {"id": 11871, "content": "社交圈总想文艺范起来，脑洞大开，往死里作，往往一条动态要编辑1小时！", "image": null, "praise_count": 146, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 2932}, {"id": 11872, "content": "写了一个百日计划，在朋友圈打卡。", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 187417}, {"id": 11873, "content": "仰天大笑十分钟", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 188017}, {"id": 11874, "content": "每天背好多书去图书馆，然后在那里默默的玩了一天手机……", "image": null, "praise_count": 477, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181847}, {"id": 14947, "content": "本来打算好好在家复习没想到却玩了几天手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 218643}, {"id": 11878, "content": "出去玩行李箱还放本书，带出去一页没动带回来还沾上了化妆水防晒霜什么的，作孽。", "image": null, "praise_count": 334, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118131}, {"id": 11879, "content": "卸载朋友圈一个月 外加不打一个人电话 应该有两个月了 其实感觉蛮好 渐渐会忘记", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 186617}, {"id": 11880, "content": "暑假把10斤重的电吉他和效果器从北京背回重庆，到家就没开过琴袋...", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161754z4JB1IVaSr8lAgob.jpg", "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 105318}, {"id": 11882, "content": "断了自己的退路，结果退路真的断了...", "image": null, "praise_count": 180, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 157780}, {"id": 11883, "content": "列了读书清单至今第一本都没看完", "image": null, "praise_count": 116, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147506}, {"id": 11887, "content": "下载了番茄时间之类的应用，用过一次或者完全没用过", "image": null, "praise_count": 101, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 95984}, {"id": 16751, "content": "写了整整的一大本日记开骂自己 自残 怎么堕落怎么玩 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 246421}, {"id": 11892, "content": "很酷的叫朋友看我跳大水坑，然后掉进去了。。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 188092}, {"id": 11895, "content": "一怒之下把那些个什么都删除了，然后后悔不已重新下载。", "image": null, "praise_count": 40, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 176412}, {"id": 11897, "content": "看了下面的描述发现我已经战胜了自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 99741}, {"id": 11898, "content": "发朋友圈天天打卡微习惯，结果还是熬夜熬成?", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115409}, {"id": 11899, "content": "头天晚上信誓旦旦第二天要早读，第二天掐紫自己爬起来确实读了，然而上午的课全都睡过去l??", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 186762}, {"id": 13693, "content": "考完四级下定决心下次一定要看书复习要考过，然而…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 199402}, {"id": 14973, "content": "难道不应该有看了小视频以后的圣人感想吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 229639}, {"id": 11905, "content": "自我安慰我很棒", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179217}, {"id": 11906, "content": "把度盘的资源删了，不够一天又默默到回收站找回", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 40841}, {"id": 11907, "content": "嘴里吐槽着前任多极品，心里却不能忘怀。", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 188300}, {"id": 11908, "content": "撸完了，发誓下次再也不撸了。下次还撸", "image": null, "praise_count": 97, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 188303}, {"id": 11909, "content": "写的计划书，从来不按计划走", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 48543}, {"id": 15749, "content": "和他斗气决定再不理他可是坚持长不过一天", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 237154}, {"id": 11911, "content": "强忍着戒撸，然而一个星期后。。。并没有什么卵用", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149115}]}